data.description: Diamond in the rough. Bring your decorating ideas and make this your dream come true. Hard to find ranch home on a country acre of flat land! Popular floor plan offers Living room / dining room and generous Family room with a brick fireplace for those cold nights to come. Southern facing rear yard offers privacy and room for all to recreate. Lower level is a open slate ready for your ideas.
